sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant B as Browser
  participant C as BookingsProvider
  participant API as /api/bookings
  participant DB as Prisma/Postgres

  U->>B: Create booking
  B->>C: addBooking()
  C->>C: Client-side conflict check
  C->>API: POST /api/bookings
  API->>DB: Load day bookings
  API->>API: Server-side conflict check
  alt conflict
    API-->>C: 409
    C-->>B: Show conflict message
  else ok
    API->>DB: Create Booking
    API-->>C: booking
    C-->>B: Update UI
  end
